biotools.summary:
Attacks on genetic privacy via uploads to genealogical databases.

Create figures for "Attacks on genetic privacy via uploads to genealogical databases" by Michael D. Edge and Graham Coop.

README for gedmatch figures & emails.

The files marked GEDmatch_*_Redacted.pdf are printouts of the display of the GEDmatch 1-to-1 match genome browser.
